---
title: Ras El Hanout Beef Meatballs with Couscous & Flaked Almonds
description: Roll up for our latest take on meatballs – a Moroccan version with ras el hanout! This exotic spice blend gives them an abundance of flavour, and we've added couscous studded with baby spinach and mint to round out the meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dfb03ab1ffc032efe010af5-d4bdffc3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/ras-el-hanout-beef-meatballs-5dfb03ab1ffc032efe010af5-6828ba1c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/ras-el-hanout-beef-meatballs-5dfb03ab1ffc032efe010af5
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: Middle East
nutrition:
  calories: 3180 kcal
